.RS 2
Returns the current call stack back-trace (
\fIstacktrace\fR) of the process. The stack has the same format as in the \fIcatch\fR part of a \fItry\fR. See The call-stack back trace (stacktrace). The depth of the stacktrace is truncated according to the \fIbacktrace_depth\fR system flag setting.

