\fIModule\fR is the \fIerror_handler\fR module used by the process (for undefined function calls, for example).

.RE

{garbage_collection, GCInfo}
.RS 2

\fIGCInfo\fR is a list containing miscellaneous information about garbage collection for this process. The content of \fIGCInfo\fR can be changed without prior notice.

.RE

{garbage_collection_info, GCInfo}
.RS 2

\fIGCInfo\fR is a list containing miscellaneous detailed information about garbage collection for this process. The content of \fIGCInfo\fR can be changed without prior notice. For details about the meaning of each item, see \fIgc_minor_start\fR in \fItrace:process/4\fR.

.RE

